com.camerontec.util.jmx.cascading.agent

Class CascadingMBeanServerForwarder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.util.jmx.DefaultMBeanServerForwarder
      • com.camerontec.util.jmx.cascading.agent.CascadingMBeanServerForwarder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MBeanServer, MBeanServerConnection, MBeanServerForwarder

    public final class CascadingMBeanServerForwarder
extends DefaultMBeanServerForwarder
    MBeanServerForwarder implementation that allows cascading clients to take advantage of a number of performance optimizations exposed by augmenting the management interface of the MBean server delegate:
    • Batched retrieval of the object names and MBeanInfo of all registered MBeans.
    • Multiplexing of all MBean notifications.
    An instance of this class should be attached to a JMX connector server via its JMXConnectorServer.setMBeanServerForwarder(javax.management.remote.MBeanServerForwarder) method.
